Notes: Chico State wins its 14th straight home opener. Jazmine Miller matches her
career high with 20 points, while Analise Riezebos pulls down a personal best
15 rebounds. The Wildcats take on Humboldt State Saturday at 5:30 p.m.
Game.Officials: Alex Moreno,  Jeff Yamaoka,  Pete Campbell
